<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>quán néng de zhǔ yé sū 迦南328</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 quán néng de zhǔ yé sū, quán néng de zhǔ yé sū,
 nǐ shì tiān shàng de jī dū, de shàng de jiù zhǔ,
 wǒ men yī shēng yǒu nǐ ya zuì yǒu fú, wǒ men yī shēng yǒu nǐ ya zuì yǒu fú,
 shēng mìng píng ān quán dé zhe, quán ya quán dé zhe,
 zhè fú zhè fú duō shǎo róng huá fù guì yě bù néng mǎi zhe,
 zhè fú zhè fú shì tiān shàng zuì dà de fú.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>328</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
</song>